data.description: Stunning South Jordan townhome now available! This beautiful home features a two car garage! As you walk inside, you will be greeted with a large family room that showcases an open Layout. The family room is large and offers tons of natural light and a ceiling fan. The kitchen is good sized and features a two tiered Island, a bar seating stools area and tile floors. On the main level enjoy the convenience of the half bathroom and laundry room space. Upstairs, you will be greeted with three bedrooms and a full bath. The master bedroom showcases a lovely Romeo and Juliet balcony. Enjoy the en suite full bath that features a walk-in closet. This home also features a large open patio that's perfect for hosting family and friends for a fun barbecue. Buyer and Buyers agent to verify all information. Square footage figures are provided as a courtesy estimate only. Buyer is advised to obtain an independent measurement.
